<p>Elsewhere former Strictly professional Janette Manrara wrote: 'Oh she cute!!!! HAPPY BIRTHDAY SIS!!'</p>

<p>While Heart Radio colleague Jenni Falconer added:  'Happy birthday gorgeous girl!'  </p>

<p>Details: Ashley completed the stunning look with black sunglasses and a stylish quilted leather bag </p>

<p>It's a look! The presenter rocked a stylish side fringe during her outing the day after her birthday celebrations</p>

